text: Laraesima albosignata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1885. It is known from Guatemala.BioLib.cz - Laraesima albosignata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1885
